requests.name: Get Athlete Stats
requests.description: Returns the activity stats of an athlete.

queryParams.description: The identifier of the athlete. Must match the authenticated athlete.

requests.name: Get Authenticated Athlete
requests.description: Returns the currently authenticated athlete. Tokens with profile:read_all scope will receive a detailed athlete representation; all others will receive a summary representation.

requests.name: Update Athlete
requests.description: Update the currently authenticated athlete. Requires profile:write scope.

queryParams.description: The weight of the athlete in kilograms.

requests.name: Get Zones
requests.description: Returns the the authenticated athlete's heart rate and power zones. Requires profile:read_all.

requests.name: Get Segment
requests.description: Returns the specified segment. read_all scope required in order to retrieve athlete-specific segment information, or to retrieve private segments.

queryParams.description: The identifier of the athlete. Must match the authenticated athlete.

requests.name: List Starred Segments
requests.description: List of the authenticated athlete's starred segments. Private segments are filtered out unless requested by a token with read_all scope.

requests.name: Star Segment
requests.description: Stars/Unstars the given segment for the authenticated athlete. Requires profile:write scope.

queryParams.description: The identifier of the athlete. Must match the authenticated athlete.
If true, star the segment; if false, unstar the segment.

requests.name: Get Segment Leaderboard
requests.description: Returns the specified segment leaderboard.

queryParams.description: The identifier of the athlete. Must match the authenticated athlete.
Filter by gender.
Summit Feature. Filter by age group.
Summit Feature. Filter by weight class.
Filter by friends of the authenticated athlete.
Filter by club.
Filter by date range.

requests.name: List Segment Efforts
requests.description: Returns a set of the authenticated athlete's segment efforts for a given segment.

queryParams.description: The identifier of the athlete. Must match the authenticated athlete.

requests.name: Explore segments
requests.description: Returns the top 10 segments matching a specified query.

queryParams.description: The latitude and longitude for two points describing a rectangular boundary for the search: [southwest corner latitutde, southwest corner longitude, northeast corner latitude, northeast corner longitude]
Desired activity type.
The minimum climbing category.
The maximum climbing category.

requests.name: Get Segment Effort
requests.description: Returns a segment effort from an activity that is owned by the authenticated athlete.

queryParams.description: The identifier of the athlete. Must match the authenticated athlete.

requests.name: Get Running Race
requests.description: Returns a running race for a given identifier.

queryParams.description: The identifier of the athlete. Must match the authenticated athlete.

requests.name: List Running Races
requests.description: Returns a list running races based on a set of search criteria.

queryParams.description: Filters the list by a given year.

requests.name: Create an Activity
requests.description: Creates a manual activity for an athlete, requires activity:write scope.

queryParams.description: The name of the activity.
Type of activity. For example - Run, Ride etc.
ISO 8601 formatted date time.
In seconds.
Description of the activity.
In meters.
Set to 1 to mark as a trainer activity.
List of native photo ids to attach to the activity.
Set to 1 to mark as commute.

requests.name: Get Activity
requests.description: Returns the given activity that is owned by the authenticated athlete. Requires activity:read for Everyone and Followers activities. Requires activity:read_all for Only Me activities.

queryParams.description: The identifier of the athlete. Must match the authenticated athlete.
To include all segments efforts.

requests.name: Update Activity
requests.description: Updates the given activity that is owned by the authenticated athlete. Requires activity:write. Also requires activity:read_all in order to update Only Me activities

queryParams.description: The identifier of the athlete. Must match the authenticated athlete.

requests.name: List Athlete Activities
requests.description: Returns the activities of an athlete for a specific identifier. Requires activity:read. Only Me activities will be filtered out unless requested by a token with activity:read_all.

queryParams.description: An epoch timestamp to use for filtering activities that have taken place before a certain time.
An epoch timestamp to use for filtering activities that have taken place after a certain time.

requests.name: List Activity Laps
requests.description: Returns the laps of an activity identified by an identifier. Requires activity:read for Everyone and Followers activities. Requires activity:read_all for Only Me activities.

queryParams.description: The identifier of the athlete. Must match the authenticated athlete.

requests.name: Get Activity Zones
requests.description: Summit Feature. Returns the zones of a given activity. Requires activity:read for Everyone and Followers activities. Requires activity:read_all for Only Me activities.

queryParams.description: The identifier of the athlete. Must match the authenticated athlete.

requests.name: List Activity Comments
requests.description: Returns the comments on the given activity. Requires activity:read for Everyone and Followers activities. Requires activity:read_all for Only Me activities.

queryParams.description: The identifier of the athlete. Must match the authenticated athlete.

requests.name: List Activity Kudoers
requests.description: Returns the athletes who kudoed an activity identified by an identifier. Requires activity:read for Everyone and Followers activities. Requires activity:read_all for Only Me activities.

queryParams.description: The identifier of the athlete. Must match the authenticated athlete.

requests.name: Get Club
requests.description: Returns a given club using its identifier.

queryParams.description: The identifier of the athlete. Must match the authenticated athlete.

requests.name: List Club Members
requests.description: Returns a list of the athletes who are members of a given club.

queryParams.description: The identifier of the athlete. Must match the authenticated athlete.

requests.name: List Club Administrators.
requests.description: Returns a list of the administrators of a given club.

queryParams.description: The identifier of the athlete. Must match the authenticated athlete.

requests.name: List Club Activities
requests.description: Retrieve recent activities from members of a specific club. The authenticated athlete must belong to the requested club in order to hit this endpoint. Pagination is supported. Athlete profile visibility is respected for all activities.

queryParams.description: The identifier of the athlete. Must match the authenticated athlete.

requests.name: List Athlete Clubs
requests.description: Returns a list of the clubs whose membership includes the authenticated athlete.

requests.name: Get Equipment
requests.description: Returns an equipment using its identifier.

queryParams.description: The identifier of the athlete. Must match the authenticated athlete.

requests.name: Get Route
requests.description: Returns a route using its identifier. Requires read_all scope for private routes.

queryParams.description: The identifier of the athlete. Must match the authenticated athlete.

requests.name: List Athlete Routes
requests.description: Returns a list of the routes created by the authenticated athlete using their athlete ID. Private routes are filtered out unless requested by a token with read_all scope.

queryParams.description: The identifier of the athlete. Must match the authenticated athlete.

requests.name: Export Route GPX
requests.description: Returns a GPX file of the route. Requires read_all scope for private routes.

queryParams.description: The identifier of the athlete. Must match the authenticated athlete.

requests.name: Export Route TCX
requests.description: Returns a TCX file of the route. Requires read_all scope for private routes.

queryParams.description: The identifier of the athlete. Must match the authenticated athlete.

requests.name: Upload Activity
requests.description: Uploads a new data file to create an activity from. Requires activity:write scope.

queryParams.description: The uploaded file.
The name of the activity.
Description of the activity.
Set to 1 to mark as a trainer activity.
Set to 1 to mark as commute.
The format of the uploaded file.
The desired external identifier of the resulting activity.

requests.name: Get Upload
requests.description: Returns an upload for a given identifier. Requires activity:write scope.

queryParams.description: The identifier of the upload.

requests.name: Get Activity Streams
requests.description: Returns the given activity's streams. Requires activity:read scope. Requires activity:read_all scope for Only Me activities.

queryParams.description: The identifier of the athlete. Must match the authenticated athlete.
Desired stream types.
Must be true.

requests.name: Get Segment Effort Streams
requests.description: Returns a set of streams for a segment effort completed by the authenticated athlete. Requires read_all scope.

queryParams.description: The identifier of the athlete. Must match the authenticated athlete.
Desired stream types.
Must be true.

requests.name: Get Segment Streams
requests.description: Returns the given segment's streams. Requires read_all scope for private segments.

queryParams.description: The identifier of the athlete. Must match the authenticated athlete.
Desired stream types.
Must be true.

requests.name: Get Route Streams
requests.description: Returns the given route's streams. Requires read_all scope for private routes.

queryParams.description: The identifier of the athlete. Must match the authenticated athlete.
